    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, keeping it in pristine shape inside and out. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this flawless ride. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look or go for a spin!",
