    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, meticulously preserved by a single owner in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from even the slightest swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery still carries that distinct factory aroma, with zero bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of service records documenting a life of preventative maintenance. This isn't just a used car; it is a pristine example for the most demanding enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
